{"id": "rios016", "name": "Audio_TVstation_497_04_03", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya!? Katsuya!?\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizens"], "content": "Run!!!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Bang"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Waahhh!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "Conflict detected, you are in violation of the Public Assembly Act, please disperse immediately.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Eh? I-I didn't do anything...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "... Is that you? Yazawa Rin...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Eh...?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "Don't be scared, you'll be able to see your mom and dad soon.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\nYou... you're the one Unit 10 told me about...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Draws Gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......! No...!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Rin!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Waahh!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Run, now!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "Sprints"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "... Hmph.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya, you're injured!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "It's nothing! Huff...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Where's your mom and dad...?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "They...<i>*sob*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... No...? It can't be...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin... get ready. Tonight, it's going down...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Going down...?\nEh!? A gun!?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "I'm sorry, I lied... this event, it was to draw the Blessed in... Our leader got their communication records. They knew we were holding an event, planned on causing a riot from within...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Never thought that they'd fire on the crowd... But we've already found their meeting location, it's just... ugh...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "You... what are you saying? I have no idea what you're talking about! Your injury...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin! Listen to me... This is our last chance... at revenge, for what the Blessed did to our family... We must make them pay! They must be eliminated! It doesn't matter if anyone else understands, this is for all of mankind!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Oh...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Think about your mom and dad! Don't you want justice!?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "But using violence...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "There's already... no other way! Listen, we already know exactly how many of them there are. We must root them out, then we'll be one step closer to our goal!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...<i>*sob*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......!\nI'm sorry... I lied to you, got you into such a dangerous situation...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya... There must be another way.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "The Blessed you saw at the television station... That's the one that worked at your parent's institute, right? I'm afraid he might have had something to do with their deaths, you must at least get him... If you don't want to join then I won't force you, but I'm going back.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... I can't let you go alone.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "I'm not alone... all of us who've become victims because of the Architects... the organization will be with me!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... I can't... let you go alone! I'm going with you...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\nYou ready?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... Yeah.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！克也！？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民たち"], "content": "逃げろ！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "ぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "きゃあ！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "市民同士の衝突を確認。\n公安条例に違反しています。\nただちに解散してください。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "え？\nわ、私はなにも……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……お前は……矢澤凛……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "え……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "怖がることはない。\nすぐに両親に会わせてやる。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\nあなた……10号機が言ってたあの……！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃を構える"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！やめ……っ！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">凛！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "きゃあ！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">逃げるぞ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……ふん。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！ケガしてる！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "大丈夫だ！\nフゥ……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "おじさんとおばさんは……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "2人は……っ……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……そんな……嘘でしょ？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛……今夜だ……今夜実行する……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "実行って……え！？銃！？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "騙してごめん……\n今日の活動は祝福されし者をおびき出すことが目的だったんだ……\nリーダーがやつらの情報を掴んで……奴らは今回の活動の最中に混乱を引き起こす気だって分かって……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "まさかいきなり攻撃してくるとは思ってなかった……\nでも、やつらの拠点はわかった……ただ……っ！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "な、にを……言ってるの？\nわかん、ないよ……\nねぇ、その傷……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛！聞いてくれ……最後のチャンスなんだ……奴らに復讐する最後の……！\nやつらが俺の家族にしたことは……許せない……！必ず代償を払わせる！\nやつらは消えてしかるべきなんだよ！\n誰にも理解されなかったとしても！これは人類のためなんだ！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "う……っ\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "なあ！\n家族のことを考えてみろよ！\nそう思うだろ！？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "でも、武力でなんて……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "もう、引き返せない……！\n組織はやつらの正確な数まで割り出してる。\n向こうの数は多くない。\nやつらを倒せば、目標に1歩近づくんだよ！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……うう……っ……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……！\nごめん……俺が、騙したから……凛までこんな危険な目に合わせてる……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也……やめよう？\nね？絶対他に方法はあるはずだから……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "さっき広場にいたあいつ……\n凛のお父さんの研究所で働いてたことがあるやつだろ？\nもしかしたらあの火事にも何か関係してるのかも……\nなら、少なくともあいつだけは……\n凛、もしイヤなら無理強いはしない。でも俺は行くよ。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……克也を、一人で行かせるわけにはいかないよ。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "俺は一人じゃない……\n俺みたいにアーキテクトの被害に遭った組織のみんながいる……！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……克也一人では……行かせられない！\n私も行く……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "………\n準備はできたか？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……うん。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！？克也！？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民們"], "content": "快跑啊！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "撞擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇啊！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "發現衝突，你們已經違反集會遊行法，請立刻解散。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦？我、我什麼都沒……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……是妳？矢澤凜……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "別怕，妳很快就能去見爸媽了。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n你就是……十號機說的……！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！不……！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">凜！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哇啊！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">快跑！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……哼。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也，你受傷了！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "小事！呼……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "叔叔跟阿姨呢……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "他們……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……不會吧……？騙人……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凜……準備好了，晚上要行動……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "行動……？\n咦！？槍！？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "對不起，我騙了妳……其實這場活動，就是為了引那些眷顧者出來……領導者截獲了他們的通訊紀錄，他們知道我們要舉辦活動，想從中作亂……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "沒想到他們會在活動上就大動槍火……但我們已經查到他們聚集的地方了，只是……唔……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "你……到底在說什麼？我完全沒有跟上！你的傷……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凜！聽我說……這是最後一次……報仇的機會了，眷顧者對我們的家人做的事情……必須付出代價！他們必須消失！不管其他人懂不懂，這麼做都是為了人類！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "想想妳爸媽！妳不想討個公道嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "但是用武力……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "我們已經……沒有回頭路了！聽好，組織的人連他們確定的數量都查出來了，人數並不多，只要能剷除他們，就離目標更近一步了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……！\n抱歉……是我騙了妳，讓妳也陷入這麼危險的處境……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也……不要，一定還有別的方法的。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "妳在廣場看到的那個眷顧者……是以前在你爸媽那邊工作過的傢伙吧？恐怕他們的死他也有份，至少要把他……妳不敢加入我也不會勉強妳，但我還是會去的。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我不能讓你一個人去。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "我不是一個人……和我一樣因為建造者受害的人……整個組織都跟我一起！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我不能……讓你一個人去！我會跟你去……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n準備好了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya!? Katsuya!?\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민들"], "content": "도망쳐!!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "으아아아!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "충돌 발생, 여러분은 폭력을 동원하였으므로 시위법을 위반하였습니다. 지금 당장 해산하십시오.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "어? 나, 나는 아무짓도 안 했는데...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "...너로군? Yazawa Rin...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "네...?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "겁먹지 마라. 너도 곧 네 부모님을 만나게 될 테니까.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n네... 네가... 10호기가 말했던...!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "총을 꺼낸다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n안 돼...!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Rin!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "으아아아!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">도망쳐!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "달린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "......흥.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya, 너... 다쳤잖아!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "괜찮아! 하아...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아저씨랑 아주머니는...?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "부모님은... 흐흑...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...설마...? 거짓말이지...?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin... 준비는 끝났어. 오늘 밤 행동 개시다...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "행동...?\n헉...!? 초... 총!?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "미안해. 널 속였어... 사실은 이 연설 행사는... 그 권고자들을 유인하기 위한 미끼였었어... 우리 리더가 그 녀석들의 통신 기록을 입수했는데, 녀석들은 우리들이 이 행사를 열 것을 알고 있었어... 그래서 그저 행사를 망치게 할 것이라고는 생각은 했지만...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "그런 행사 중에 대놓고 총기를 사용할 줄은 생각도 못했어... 하지만 지금 우리들은 녀석들이 모인 곳을 알아냈어... 다만... 으윽...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "너... 대체 무슨 말이야, 그게! 하나도 못 알아 듣겠잖아! 그리고 니 상처...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin! 내 말 잘 들어! 이것이... 복수할 수 있는 마지막 기회야. 권고자들이 우리 가족들에게 한 짓... 반드시 되갚아 주겠어! 그 녀석들은 모두 사라져야만 해! 다른 사람들이 이해해주든 못하든 이젠 상관없어! 어차피 이것들은 모두 인류를 위한 일이니까!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "윽......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "네 부모님 일을 생각해봐!\n그게 어쩔 수 없는 사고였다고 생각하는 거야!?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "하지만 폭력을 사용하는 것은...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "우리들은 이미... 돌아갈 수 없는 강을 건넜어! 잘 들어! 조직의 사람들이 이미 녀석들의 숫자까지 정확히 알아냈어. 녀석들의 수는 얼마 되지 않아! 그 녀석들만 제거하면, 우리들은 목표에 한걸음 더 다가갈 수 있는 거야!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......흑......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......!\n 미안해... 네게 거짓말해서... 결국 너를 이런 위험한 상황에 휘말리게 만들어버렸구나...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya... 하지 마. 분명 다른 방법도 있을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "광장에서 봤던 그 권고자... 예전에 네 부모님이 일하시던 연구소에서 봤던 아키텍트잖아? 분명 네 부모님의 죽음도 그 녀석들과... 아니, 그 녀석만큼은 확실히 관여했을 거야... 네가 함께하지 않겠다면, 나도 강요할 생각은 없어. 하지만 나는 가야만 해.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......너 혼자 가게 둘 순 없어.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "혼자가 아니야... 나와 같은 아키텍트의 피해자와... 조직의 모든 동료들이 나와 함께할 거니까!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...너... 너 혼자서 가게 둘 수는 없어! 나... 나도 같이 갈게...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n준비됐어?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......응.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！？克也！？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民們"], "content": "快跑啊！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "撞擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇啊！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "發現衝突，你們已經違反集會遊行法，請立刻解散。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦？我、我什麼都沒……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……是妳？矢澤凜……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "別怕，妳很快就能去見爸媽了。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n你就是……十號機說的……！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！不……！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">凜！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哇啊！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": 