"type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也……不要，一定還有別的方法的。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "妳在廣場看到的那個眷顧者……是以前在你爸媽那邊工作過的傢伙吧？恐怕他們的死他也有份，至少要把他……妳不敢加入我也不會勉強妳，但我還是會去的。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我不能讓你一個人去。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "我不是一個人……和我一樣因為建造者受害的人……整個組織都跟我一起！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我不能……讓你一個人去！我會跟你去……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n準備好了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！ ？克也！ ？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民们"], "content": "快跑啊！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "撞击"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇啊！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "发现冲突，你们已经违反集会游行法，请立刻解散。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦？我、我什么都没……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……是妳？矢泽凛……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "别怕，妳很快就能去见爸妈了。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n你就是……十号机说的……！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "举枪"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！不……！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">凛！ ！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "哇啊！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">快跑！ ！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……哼。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也，你受伤了！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "小事！呼……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "叔叔跟阿姨呢……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "他们……呜……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……不会吧……？骗人……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛……准备好了，晚上要行动……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "行动……？\n咦！ ？枪！ ？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "对不起，我骗了妳……其实这场活动，就是为了引那些眷顾者出来……领导者截获了他们的通讯纪录，他们知道我们要举办活动，想从中作乱……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "没想到他们会在活动上就大动枪火……但我们已经查到他们聚集的地方了，只是……唔……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "你……到底在说什么？我完全没有跟上！你的伤……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛！听我说……这是最后一次……报仇的机会了，眷顾者对我们的家人做的事情……必须付出代价！他们必须消失！不管其他人懂不懂，这么做都是为了人类！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "想想妳爸妈！妳不想讨个公道吗！ ？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "但是用武力……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "我们已经……没有回头路了！听好，组织的人连他们确定的数量都查出来了，人数并不多，只要能铲除他们，就离目标更近一步了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……呜……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……！\n抱歉……是我骗了妳，让妳也陷入这么危险的处境……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也……不要，一定还有别的方法的。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "妳在广场看到的那个眷顾者……是以前在你爸妈那边工作过的家伙吧？恐怕他们的死他也有份，至少要把他……妳不敢加入我也不会勉强妳，但我还是会去的。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我不能让你一个人去。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "我不是一个人……和我一样因为建造者受害的人……整个组织都跟我一起！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我不能……让你一个人去！我会跟你去……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n准备好了吗？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}